  "sketchCode": "// Example: Buzzer Melody\n// Play three notes using tone() on pin 8.\n\nint buzzerPin = 8;\n\nvoid setup() {\n  pinMode(buzzerPin, OUTPUT);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  tone(buzzerPin, 262); // C4\n  delay(500);\n  tone(buzzerPin, 330); // E4\n  delay(500);\n  tone(buzzerPin, 392); // G4\n  delay(500);\n  noTone(buzzerPin);\n  delay(1000);\n}\n",
